# Events Directory

This directory contains event files for the event module.

## Purpose

Event files define domain events that occur within the application. These events are used to decouple components and enable event-driven architecture.

## Structure

Each event file should:

- Extend the base event class
- Define the event payload interface
- Include relevant metadata (timestamp, aggregate ID, etc.)

## Usage

Events are typically emitted by aggregate roots or services and consumed by event handlers to trigger side effects or update read models.
